ts\" title=\"Internship Placements\">Internship Placements<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/unilever-canada-internship\/#Eligibility_Criteria_to_Apply_to_the_Unilever_Internship_Program\" title=\"Eligibility Criteria to Apply to the Unilever Internship Program\">Eligibility Criteria to Apply to the Unilever Internship Program<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Visit the Unilever Canada\u00a0 Website<strong><a href=\"https:\/\/careers.unilever.com\/united-states-and-canada\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">\u00a0https:\/\/careers.unilever.com\/united-states-and-canada<\/a><\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"details-of-the-scholarship\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Details_of_the_Scholarship\"><\/span>Details of the Scholarship<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3 id=\"benefits-of-working-in-unilever\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Benefits_of_Working_in_Unilever\"><\/span><strong>Benefits of Working in Unilever<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Employment<\/strong>: An internship at Unilever will lead to Employment.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Compensation<\/strong>: You\u2019ll be offered a competitive salary right away.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Growth and Learning<\/strong>: With hands-on exposure, mentoring, and practical work. Undoubtedly, you will learn and work with the best people under a Unilever Internship 2024.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Unilever Internship Salary<\/strong>: All interns will receive a monthly salary and other facilities like Gym, health, and medical exams.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Break<\/strong>: Unilever provides 25 days of holiday + bank holidays.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id=\"internship-areas\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Internship_Areas\"><\/span><strong>Internship Areas:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Marketing<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Research &amp; Development<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Customer Development<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Finance<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Supply Chain<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Human Resources<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Communications<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Information Technology<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Legal<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Ben and Jerry\u2019s Factory<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Procurement<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id=\"opportunities-in-unilever\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Opportunities_in_Unilever\"><\/span><strong>Opportunities in Unilever<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Unilever offers two types of Opportunities. 1) For Fresh Students to Start a Career. 2) Experienced Careers.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>For Fresh Students:<\/strong>\u00a0Range of graduate and internship opportunities around the world.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Careers:<\/strong>\u00a0For Professionals with working experience.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id=\"internship-placements\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Internship_Placements\"><\/span><strong>Internship Placements<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>There are two types of Placements:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><b>Summer Placement:\u00a0<\/b>12-week internship beginning in June.<\/li>\n<li><b>Industrial Placement:\u00a0<\/b>A 12-month placement in a specialized role that begins in June for students<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id=\"eligibility-criteria-to-apply-to-the-unilever-internship-program\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Eligibility_Criteria_to_Apply_to_the_Unilever_Internship_Program\"><\/span><strong>Eligibility Criteria to Apply to the Unilever Internship Program<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Any student from any country can apply. Unilever works in more than 190 countries.<\/li>\n<li>A minimum bachelor\u2019s degree is required in any field or discipline.<\/li>\n<li>The internship details and criteria vary and are different for each position.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Company: Unilever, Level: Undergraduates, Graduates, Location: Global, Deadline: No. How to Apply for the Unilever Internship 2024? The&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":18367,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[14],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9703"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=9703"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9703\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":18368,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9703\/revisions\/18368"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/18367"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=9703"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=9703"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=9703"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}